title: BRIEF-Umanis H1 net profit group share up at 1.7 million euros
text:
BRIEF-Umanis H1 net profit group share up at 1.7 million euros 
Oct 2 Umanis SA : 
* H1 revenue 74.1 million euros ($82.7 million) vs 67.6 million euros year ago 
* H1 operating income 2.9 million euros vs 2.2 million euros year ago 
* H1 net profit group share 1.7 million euros vs 1.5 million euros year ago 
($1 = 0.8961 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
